Datasource.Parameter: ( SELECT geometry, area, type FROM osm_landusages ORDER BY area DESC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('river', 'canal') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('river', 'canal', 'stream') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, area, type FROM osm_landusages WHERE type = 'nature_reserve' ORDER BY area DESC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, "type" AS type , "building:levels" AS building_levels FROM osm_buildings WHERE type NOT IN ('0','false', 'no') ORDER BY ST_YMin(ST_Envelope(geometry)) DESC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_aeroways WHERE type IN ('apron', 'runway', 'taxiway') ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, 0 AS bridge, access, render, layer, 1 as tunnel, CASE WHEN type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') THEN 'motorway' WHEN type IN ('primary', 'secondary') THEN 'mainroad' WHEN type IN ('motorway_link', 'trunk_link', 'primary_link', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street') THEN 'minorroad' WHEN type IN ('service', 'track') THEN 'service' WHEN type IN ('path', 'cycleway', 'footway', 'pedestrian', 'steps', 'bridleway') THEN 'noauto' WHEN type IN ('light_rail', 'subway', 'narrow_gauge', 'rail', 'tram') THEN 'railway' ELSE 'other' END AS stylegroup FROM ( SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '1_outline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE tunnel NOT IN (0) UNION ALL SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '2_line' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE tunnel NOT IN (0) UNION ALL SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '3_inline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE tunnel NOT IN (0) ) AS tunnels ORDER BY layer ASC , render ASC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry FROM osm_roads WHERE type = 'turning_circle' ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, 0 AS tunnel, 0 AS bridge, access, 'fill' AS render, CASE WHEN type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') THEN 'motorway' WHEN type IN ('primary', 'secondary') THEN 'mainroad' WHEN type IN ('motorway_link', 'trunk_link', 'primary_link', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street') THEN 'minorroad' WHEN type IN ('service', 'track') THEN 'service' WHEN type IN ('path', 'cycleway', 'footway', 'pedestrian', 'steps', 'bridleway') THEN 'noauto' WHEN type IN ('light_rail', 'subway', 'narrow_gauge', 'rail', 'tram','abandoned','disused') THEN 'railway' ELSE 'other_rail' END AS stylegroup FROM osm_roads WHERE (type IS NOT NULL) AND (tunnel IS NULL OR tunnel = 0) AND (bridge IS NULL OR bridge = 0) ORDER BY z_order ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type FROM osm_roads WHERE type IN ('motorway', 'trunk', 'primary', 'secondary', 'motorway_link', 'trunk_link') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type, bridge, tunnel FROM osm_roads WHERE type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, type AS type, bridge, tunnel FROM osm_roads WHERE type IN ('rail') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry FROM osm_roads WHERE type = 'turning_circle' ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, 1 AS bridge, access, render, layer, 0 as tunnel, CASE WHEN type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') THEN 'motorway' WHEN type IN ('primary', 'secondary') THEN 'mainroad' WHEN type IN ('motorway_link', 'trunk_link', 'primary_link', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street') THEN 'minorroad' WHEN type IN ('service', 'track') THEN 'service' WHEN type IN ('path', 'cycleway', 'footway', 'pedestrian', 'steps', 'bridleway') THEN 'noauto' WHEN type IN ('light_rail', 'subway', 'narrow_gauge', 'rail', 'tram') THEN 'railway' ELSE 'other' END AS stylegroup FROM ( SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '1_outline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge NOT IN (0) UNION ALL SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '2_line' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge NOT IN (0) UNION ALL SELECT geometry, type, access, layer, '3_inline' AS render FROM osm_roads WHERE bridge NOT IN (0) ) AS bridges ORDER BY layer ASC, render ASC ) AS data
( SELECT geometry, admin_level FROM osm_admin WHERE type = 'administrative' AND admin_level IN ('2', '4') ) AS data

(SELECT geometry, type, name, "name:en", z_order, population, CASE WHEN ("name:en" NOT LIKE '') AND ("name" NOT LIKE CONCAT('%',"name:en",'%')) THEN CONCAT(U&'\200E',name, U&'\200E',E'\n', '(', "name:en",')') ELSE name END AS iname FROM osm_places ORDER BY population DESC NULLS LAST ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, CASE WHEN ("name:en" NOT LIKE '') AND ("name" NOT LIKE CONCAT('%',"name:en",'%')) THEN CONCAT(U&'\200E',name, U&'\200E',E' ', '(', "name:en",')') ELSE name END AS name , ref, oneway, CHAR_LENGTH(ref) AS reflen FROM osm_roads WHERE type IN ('motorway', 'trunk') AND (name IS NOT NULL OR ref IS NOT NULL) ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, CASE WHEN ("name:en" NOT LIKE '') AND ("name" NOT LIKE CONCAT('%',"name:en",'%')) THEN CONCAT(U&'\200E',name, U&'\200E',E' ', '(', "name:en",')') ELSE name END AS name , oneway FROM osm_roads WHERE (name IS NOT NULL OR oneway IN (1,-1)) AND type IN ('primary', 'secondary', 'tertiary') ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, CASE WHEN ("name:en" NOT LIKE '') AND ("name" NOT LIKE CONCAT('%',"name:en",'%')) THEN CONCAT(U&'\200E',name, U&'\200E',E' ', '(', "name:en",')') ELSE name END AS name , oneway FROM osm_roads WHERE (name IS NOT NULL OR oneway IN (1, -1)) AND type IN ('residential', 'unclassified', 'road', 'living_street', 'unknown') ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, CASE WHEN ("name:en" NOT LIKE '') AND ("name" NOT LIKE CONCAT('%',"name:en",'%')) THEN CONCAT(U&'\200E',name, U&'\200E',E' ', '(', "name:en",')') ELSE name END AS name FROM osm_waterways WHERE type IN ('canal', 'river', 'stream') AND name IS NOT NULL ) AS data

( SELECT geometry, type, type AS "addr:housenumber" FROM osm_housenumbers_ways WHERE type NOT IN ('0','false', 'no') UNION SELECT geometry, type, CASE WHEN name NOT LIKE '' /*AND length(name)<10 THEN name*/ THEN '' ELSE type END AS "addr:housenumber" FROM osm_housenumbers WHERE type NOT IN ('0','false', 'no') ) AS data
( SELECT geometry FROM osm_housenumbers_interpolated WHERE type NOT IN ('0','false', 'no') ) AS data
